{"tid":2195315,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中國新聞】　恒大：全國樓盤全綫7折促銷","createTime":"2020-09-09T05:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T12:59:40.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6cfa48774720aec53fe435d896b069bed982be16","tid":2195315,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2745733/【恒大股價】恒大全國樓盤7折\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2745733%2F%E3%80%90%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E3%80%91%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%A8%93%E7%9B%A47%E6%8A%98&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg97g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=3eddc906\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2745733/【恒大股價】恒大全國樓盤7折</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BabH2tF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBabH2tF.png&h=ddc88dca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恒大 （03333） 昨日（6日）召開集團營銷大會，據內地傳媒報道，主席許家印在會上宣布，自9月7日起至10月8日，恒大將開展新一輪促銷活動，全國樓盤全綫7折。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，恒大將下放權限，給予恒大總部和地區公司部門負責人以上領導有額外96折的簽批權限。<br />\n<br />\n恒大周一早市股價反覆，全日跌2.4%，收報16.54元，成交1.3億元。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，以一套原價100萬元的恒大房子為例，如果享有所有折扣優惠，實際購買房價約58萬元，<br />\n<br />\n恒大在今年2月13日起宣布旗下全國所有樓盤實施網上購房，並推出史無前例力度的購房促銷活動。在2月18至29日期間，恒大樓盤曾75折賣樓。<br />\n<br />\n恒大上半年業績，實現盈業收入2666億元，按年升17.5%，實現淨利潤則為147.6億元，按年下跌46%。"},{"pid":"eafec9f80c2fe8190403cdd5a34723d45bc2a6aa","tid":2195315,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6cfa48774720aec53fe435d896b069bed982be16","tid":2195315,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2745733/【恒大股價】恒大全國樓盤7折\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2745733%2F%E3%80%90%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E3%80%91%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%A8%93%E7%9B%A47%E6%8A%98&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg97g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=3edd